Subject: Re: [VB] Gear Box Maintenance

ya, and while you have the rear wheels off the ground, or even have the 
wheels off, try he rear drums for wiggle.   they should not wiggle or thunk- 
if you do you should look at new reduction bearings.  think there should only 
be a hair of wiggle- a thunk thunk is bad.  But keeping enough clean oil in 
there makes them last a long time.

